+## Supported Models
+
+From `core/models.json`, gpt-5.2-codex supports:
+- `low` — fast responses
+- `medium` — balanced (default)
+- `high` — complex problems
+- `xhigh` — extra reasoning
+
+If `reasoning_effort` is omitted in agent YAML, it inherits from parent config.
